parameters:
Only those who have been recognized can pass
beyond this point... Show me your strength. If you
can defeat me, you may proceed further...

(Now, I wonder what would be the best course of
action here...)

I understand your strength... As promised... You
may proceed...
Weak... There is no use for the weak.

If you refuse to fight... Why, a non-combatant
magical girl.

I don't like pointless fights. You seem different
from the usual magical beasts.

I am the protector of this lewd demon village. I
send away those who do not belong here, that is my
job.

And those who do not show their strength, they
cannot pass through here. Give up on passing
through here.

I have permission to enter the lewd demon village.
If a fight is necessary, I will fight. What will
you do?
You may pass because I have recognized you!

Oh, so the Imp is your ally? Hmmm, very well. I
will allow you to pass through here.
Thank you, \N[10]! With this, we can proceed.

I see, it seems you're not completely lying...
However, you may still refuse to fight me. Let's
settle this!

Hmph, you lied. Liars can be seen through in the
shadows. Prepare yourself!
If necessary, I will spar with you.
What's wrong... Show me your true power...
ボスを撃破することで、ストーンを制御できる
※このストーンの影響のある敵の制御スイッチをONにする

\C[2]The enemies in the vicinity have become
docile after being able to control this Nest Stone
with magic\C[1]!
初回は貴重なお宝出現
※基本はエピック、場合によっては固定、レジェンドなど

Do you want to release the control of the Nest
Stone? If you release it, nearby enemies will
attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!
ボスを撃破することで、ストーンを制御できる

\C[2]I controlled this Nest Stone with magic!
\C[1]The nearby enemies became docile!
そのエリアのコモンイベントを設置する

My precious gauntlet! I dropped it here... I'm
glad! Thank you, Konoha-san.
